using Makie, CairoMakie

  as = -2.2:.01:.7
  bs = -1.5:.01:1.5
  C = [a + b * im for a in as, b in bs]
  function mandelbrot(c)
    z = c
    i = 1
    while i < 100 && abs2(z) < 4
      z = z^2 + c
      i += 1
    end
    i
  end

  heatmap(as, bs, mandelbrot.(C))
